Packages 
Package Description
coppelia  
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt
This package contains all common classes, that is classes used in both the server and the app.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.callback_interfaces
Contains all public callback interfaces one can subscribe to for events of the server.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.control
This package contains classes pertaining the control flow used in both the server and the app.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.control.commands
This package contains all command types, subclasses of AbstractCommand like SetSensorCommand.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.discovery
This package contains classes pertaining the discovery system in both server and app.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.examples
Contains all of the example framework usages written by the softwareprojekt team
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.examples.graphing
The graphing package contains a simple live data plotting graph to ease development using sensor data.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.examples.gui
Contains the graphical user interface written for the three example usages
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.examples.kuka
The kuka package contains a simple control example for a kuka LBR iiwa 7.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.examples.mouse
The mouse package contains an example usage of the framework which lets you move your mouse cursor by moving your phone.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.examples.nes
The nes package contains an example of using the framework as a nes controller substitute.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.misc
This package contains miscellaneous classes.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.networking
Contains all server specific code, such as the client connections and their manager.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.pipeline
The pipeline package contains all classes used for directing or modifying the data flow.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.pipeline.filters
This package contains all filters written for the framework.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.pipeline.splitters
This package contains the pipeline splitters that have already been implemented.
de.ovgu.softwareprojekt.util
The util package contains a small amount of generic util functions.
